The paper also extensively evaluates the proposed method on classification and regression tasks, which are common applications of neural networks and fall under the categories of "machine learning" and "artificial intelligence". Additionally, the paper experiments with combining the proposed method with a deep convolutional neural network, which falls under the category of "computer vision". Finally, the paper discusses the impact of the proposed method on the number of neurons used in the network, which is a topic related to "neural networks" and "data structures".
